{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "6.640", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrter Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "6.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "14.920", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Geehrte Kolleginnen und Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "14.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "15.840", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich verstehe nicht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "15.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "24.800", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass antibiotikaresistente Bakterien in unseren Fl\u00fcssen so eine \u00dcberraschung sind. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "24.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "26.520", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Oder verstehe ich das doch? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "26.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "26.880", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "So, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "26.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "31.680", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie hier einige Fraktionen ihr Nichtstun hinter fehlendem Wissen verstecken, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "31.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "33.920", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist das ja kein Wunder."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "33.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "35.200", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Alle Bundesregierungen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "35.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "38.480", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "von GroKo bis Schwarz-Gelb, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "38.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "41.400", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "haben in ihrer Regierungszeit Ursachen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "41.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "46.760", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Entstehung und Verbreitung von multiresistenten Keimen ignoriert, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "46.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "49.920", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und das ist lebensbedrohlich. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "49.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "58.720", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "15\u00a0000\u00a0Patienten infizieren sich jedes Jahr in unseren Krankenh\u00e4usern mit multiresistenten Keimen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "58.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "64.680", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Gleichzeitig wird \u00fcber Sparma\u00dfnahmen die Hygienequalit\u00e4t zur\u00fcckgefahren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "64.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "65.760", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es wird geredet, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "65.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "67.280", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber die Hygienestandards gehen zur\u00fcck. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "67.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "71.760", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das beg\u00fcnstigt Entstehung und Ausbreitung dieser Keime."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "71.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "75.040", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Woher kommen solche Keime noch? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "75.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "76.480", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Erstens. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "76.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "81.640", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "1\u00a0700\u00a0Tonnen Antibiotika werden j\u00e4hrlich an Schweine, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "81.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "84.000", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Rinder und Gefl\u00fcgel verf\u00fcttert. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "84.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "92.760", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u00dcber die G\u00fclle gelangen die Keime plus die Medikamentenr\u00fcckst\u00e4nde in unsere Landwirtschaft und breiten sich aus, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "92.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "98.840", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und noch immer gibt es keine Liste von Medikamenten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "98.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "100.240", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die beim Menschen noch helfen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "100.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "102.600", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "deren Einsatz bei Tieren aber verboten werden sollte. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "102.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "104.200", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist ein schweres Vers\u00e4umnis."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "104.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "105.240", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zweitens. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "105.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "112.360", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es gibt noch immer kein R\u00fccknahmesystem f\u00fcr abgelaufene Altmedikamente. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "112.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "114.760", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es gibt noch immer keine Verpflichtung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "114.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "118.640", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "den Entsorgungsweg auf die Pappschachteln zu drucken. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "118.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "125.400", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch das ist Resultat der Vernachl\u00e4ssigung von Pflichten einer jeden Bundesregierung."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "125.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "128.360", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Drittens. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "128.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "137.120", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In Billiglohnl\u00e4ndern wie Indien werden Antibiotika mit riesigen Profiten produziert; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "137.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "139.840", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Abwasserreinigung und Kl\u00e4rung entfallen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "139.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "145.160", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Bei der Bev\u00f6lkerungsdichte und den Temperaturen vor Ort z\u00fcchtet man regelrecht Resistenzen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "145.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "147.880", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die dann \u00fcber Reisende nach Europa kommen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "147.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "151.640", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und die Bundesregierung schaut weg."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "151.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "152.600", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Kollege, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "152.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "156.160", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "erlauben Sie eine Zwischenfrage aus den Reihen der CDU/CSU-Fraktion?"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "159.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "160.400", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ja."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "160.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "160.960", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Kollege, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "160.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "168.600", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie sprachen von einem Einsatz von 1\u00a0734\u00a0Tonnen an Arzneimitteln in der Nutztierhaltung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "168.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "170.200", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ist Ihnen entgangen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "170.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "171.600", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die deutsche Landwirtschaft, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "171.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "179.480", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die deutschen Tierhalter diese Menge in den letzten f\u00fcnf Jahren um 53\u00a0Prozent reduziert haben? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "179.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "180.640", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich frage Sie: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "180.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "182.480", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wieso tragen Sie diese alten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "182.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "183.720", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "falschen Zahlen vor?"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "183.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "185.280", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Kollege, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "185.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "192.640", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass reduziert wurde, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "192.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "193.240", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "stimmt; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "193.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "196.400", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber 1\u00a0700 Tonnen ist die Zahl des letzten Jahres."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "196.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "200.120", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Insofern sollten Sie noch einmal nachschauen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "200.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "204.440", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Schauen Sie auch auf die Sorten der eingesetzten Medikamente. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "204.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "206.480", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Kollegin von den Gr\u00fcnen hat es ausgef\u00fchrt: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "206.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "208.560", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es sind gerade die Medikamente, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "208.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "211.560", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die beim Menschen gegen multiresistente Keime noch helfen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "211.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "214.720", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die in der Gefl\u00fcgelwirtschaft in gro\u00dfer Menge eingesetzt werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "214.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "215.680", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "215.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "217.680", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was f\u00fcr uns die Notfalloption ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "217.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "219.680", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wird also fl\u00e4chendeckend eingesetzt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "219.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "222.160", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie k\u00f6nnen doch nicht leugnen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "222.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "226.240", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die Bundesregierung keine Verbotslisten aufgestellt hat."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "226.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "240.280", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Im Jahre\u00a02017 hat meine Fraktion letztmals einen Antrag zur Einf\u00fchrung eines R\u00fccknahmesystems f\u00fcr Altmedikamente, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "240.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "241.760", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "finanziert von Pharmakonzernen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "241.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "242.560", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "eingebracht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "242.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "245.920", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Union hat ihn abgelehnt mit der Begr\u00fcndung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "245.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "249.920", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das k\u00f6nne man den Pharmaunternehmen nicht zumuten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "249.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "255.400", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Mir kommen die Tr\u00e4nen bei Jahresgewinnen in H\u00f6he von 7,3\u00a0Milliarden Euro bei Bayer, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "255.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "257.760", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "7,7\u00a0Milliarden Euro bei Novartis, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "257.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "260.360", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "4,8\u00a0Milliarden Euro bei Sanofi, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "260.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "262.360", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "7,5\u00a0Milliarden Euro bei Roche. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "262.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "264.080", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sind Sie wirklich der Meinung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "264.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "268.720", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass man denen keine 50\u00a0Millionen Euro f\u00fcr ein R\u00fccknahmesystem zumuten kann? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "268.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "270.560", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine Damen und Herren von der Union, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "270.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "272.320", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie brauchen sich nicht zu wundern, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "272.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "275.280", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir Sie als Lobbyverein der Pharmaindustrie betrachten."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "275.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "276.320", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Linke fordert, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "276.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "280.080", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass endlich Listen eingef\u00fchrt werden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "280.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "289.560", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "durch die der Antibiotikaeinsatz strenger reglementiert und der Einsatz von Reserveantibiotika in der Tiermedizin ausgeschlossen wird."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "289.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "290.640", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir fordern, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "290.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "296.160", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass endlich mehr Mittel f\u00fcr Hygiene in Krankenh\u00e4usern und im medizinischen Bereich bereitgestellt werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "296.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "301.720", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dazu geh\u00f6rt auch die Schaffung von 100\u00a0000\u00a0Stellen f\u00fcr Pflegekr\u00e4fte im Gesundheitswesen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "301.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "306.480", 
   "id": "s000085", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "damit eine gute Pflege m\u00f6glich ist und Resistenzen sich nicht weiter verbreiten."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "306.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "309.200", 
   "id": "s000086", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir fordern zudem, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "309.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "313.800", 
   "id": "s000087", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die Pharmariesen in Gesch\u00e4ftsberichten nicht nur von ihrer Verantwortung reden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "313.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "316.960", 
   "id": "s000088", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern diese Verantwortung auch \u00fcbernehmen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "316.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "320.040", 
   "id": "s000089", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "indem sie ihr Geld nicht nur in profitable Potenzmittel, "
   ]
